short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SellInsights LinkedIn Extension allows you to analyze your linkedin activities.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SellInsights Linkedin extension allows you to connect your sales team Linkedin's and learn
- Which searches were done
- How much time each agent spent on which part of LinekdIn.
- Which companies were visited
- Which users were visited
- Which posts were posted and where
- Which re-shares were done and where
- How much time each agent spent and on what
- What's their LinkedIn network growth
